Tools for managing TLFs via Radar Web Services

RadarKerberosLogin.sh
- Log into Radar using AppleConnect credentials

TaskSchedule.pl
- Generate ETAs depending on a predefined radar order
- Also shows blocking radars

TaskScheduleSmokeySpirit.pl
- Sample configuration for TaskSchedule.pl for Smokey "Spirit" TLF

ProjectTlf.pl
- Generate weekly status updates

ProjectTlfSmokeySpirit.pl
- Sample configuration for ProjectTlf.pl for Smokey "Spirit" TLF
